data.description: Quality Craftsmanship and Former Model Home with luxury and sophisticated features throughout! Situated on a large corner lot, 5 bedrooms & 5 baths, downstairs 2nd Primary/En Suite with 3/4 Bath & family room. $100K upgraded backyard: pebble tec pool with wet deck, bar top/ 4 stools, water pots/features, huge paver patio and Alumawood covered, plus full outdoor kitchen and stainless appliances to entertain inside/out. Custom staircase, mantle, and pony wall in hickory, African bubinga/limba 1" hardwood. 2 way fireplace. You'll love the neutral decor and features. The kitchen has stainless appliances including 48" 6 burner cooktop/vent, built-in fridge, oven/convection micro, large island, and open to the great room and backyard.  Spacious 2nd bedrooms with bath access. Master bedroom with marble and custom tile floors, jetted tub, and seamless glass shower enclosure. Make sure to check out the Virtual Tour Link to the Matterport walking tour to see everything about this great home.
